product_name: Ultimate Survival Technologies Paracord 550 Utility Cord - 30'
long_description: Useful for lashing gear, hanging food bags and replacing shoelaces or tent guylines, you won't regret bringing the Ultimate Survival Technologies Paracord 550 Utility Cord with you on the trail. Includes 30 ft. of 550-lb. test cord. Tease out individual threads to use as fishing line or sewing thread. Ultimate Survival Technologies Paracord 550 Utility Cord includes a carabiner for easy attachment to packs.
